main event: An unidentified flying object was sighted over Ramey AFB, Puerto Rico on April 6, 1967.
interesting points: The UFO was first seen near the enlisted men's club before moving across the area.,Witnesses observed the object for about two minutes.,The object was described as a bright, oval-shaped light.,No sound was associated with the sighting.,The UFO eventually disappeared from view to the northeast.
sighted object: a bright, oval-shaped object in the sky
witness description: several individuals near the enlisted men's club
